description: Another applicant from outside Prague. He came the long way from Teplice just to get the job. But I could see that he supposed the job to be somehow different. He was expecting rather to be in the logistic-management than working in the warehouse itself. And in my dirty offer he was also not interested. Anyway. The second guy looked even cuter. But a bit naive as well. He worked over a year as a construction-worker before. But the money was bad and the job was exhausting. So he finished there and is now looking for something new. I was really into him especially when he told me that he loves to play soccer and basketball in his spare-time. I had to see his athletic legs. And indeed he agreed to strip naked instead of paying our evil one-time-fee.
title: Dirty Scout 31
